\f1\b\fs32 \cf0 Troubleshooting
\f0\b0\fs24 \

\fs8 \
\pard\tx1440\tx2880\tx4320\tx5760\tx7200\ql\qnatural

\fs24 \cf0 DoubleCommand has been developed for Mac OS X 10.1 and above. It is known to run on Mac OS X 10.1.0 through to 10.2.3 and probably runs on later versions, too. However, since it links to internal kernel structures, newer versions of the kernel may break DoubleCommand. In particular, there are separate binaries for 10.1.0 - 10.1.4, 10.1.5 and 10.2. Versions since 1.4 only support Mac OS X 10.2.\
\
If your machine does not boot after installing DoubleCommand, hold the option (alt) key during booting and boot to Mac OS 9. You can remove DoubleCommand from Mac OS 9.\
\
